#################3 stash Command

- git stash is used when you have uncommitted changes in your working directory 
(both staged and unstaged) and you want to temporarily set them aside without committing.

git branch add

git checkout add(made some changes)

git diff

git stash save "Worked on Add function"

git diff (no changes found)

git status (nothing)

